      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;21:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/title.dita">The following attributes are available on this element: <xref class="- topic/xref " href="../attributes/universalAttributes.dita" keyref="attributes-universal" xtrc="xref:1;22:42" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/title.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>Universal attribute group<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The universal attribute group defines a set of common attributes available on most DITA     elements. The universal attribute group includes all attributes from the metadata, ID,     localization, and debug attribute groups, plus the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;8:64" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/universalAttributes.dita">class</xmlatt> attribute.</desc></xref> (without the Metadata attribute group),
          plus <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;23:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/title.dita">base</xmlatt> and <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:2;23:50" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/title.dita">rev</xmlatt> from the <xref class="- topic/xref " href="../attributes/metadataAttributes.dita" keyref="attributes-metadata" xtrc="xref:2;24:41" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/title.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>Metadata attribute group<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The metadata attribute group includes common metadata attributes, several of which     support conditional processing (filtering and flagging) or the creation of new attribute domain     specializations.</desc></xref>.</p>
